347
00:27:18,900 --> 00:27:20,100
und der Arithmetik,

348
00:27:20,300 --> 00:27:23,000
Muhammad ibn al Mussa al Koreizi.

349
00:27:23,600 --> 00:27:25,200
Von seinem Namen Al Koreizi

350
00:27:25,500 --> 00:27:27,900
